"8:52:7" : {s: 8, a: 52, w: 7, r: "كفر", t: "كَفَرُوا۟", l: "كَفَرَ", lc: 289, tl: "kafarū", lb: "অবিশ্বাস করা, ঢেকে দেওয়া",e: "They disbelieved", b: "কুফরী করেছে, অবিশ্বাস করেছে", i: "mereka mengingkari", f: 189, rm: "to conceal, to cover, to reject, to disbelieve, to be thankless, unthankful, ungrateful, to disown, deny, faithless, black horse, dark night, tiller/farmer."},
